data.description: Welcome to this charming 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home on a corner lot in a stunning neighborhood. The well-designed interior includes a spacious living room that opens up to a beautiful kitchen, a great room with french doors on the main floor, and four bedrooms on the second level. Step outside to a back deck, perfect for relaxation and enjoy fresh air! As part of the community, the HOA allows residents access to a pool and tennis courts for leisure and recreation. Washer and dryer convey with purchase of the home. Don't miss the opportunity to call this place home!
